<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - 由 RSSHub 提供支持</description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 24 Jul 2024 06:18:23 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>保时捷利润在几个月销量下降和供应链问题后下降</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/porsche-profits-drop-after-months-lower-sales-supply-chain-issues-2024-07-24/</link><description>保时捷周三表示，在经历了几个月的供应链问题和中国销量下滑等问题的困扰后，其上半年营业利润下降了 20.5%，至 30.6 亿欧元（33.2 亿美元）。</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jul 2024 06:03:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/porsche-profits-drop-after-months-lower-sales-supply-chain-issues-2024-07-24/</guid></item><item><title>东盟部长们在老挝举行会议，寻求解决缅甸危机和南海紧张局势</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/asean-seeks-tackle-myanmar-crisis-south-china-sea-tension-ministers-meet-laos-2024-07-24/</link><description>东南亚集团东盟周三在老挝举行会议，寻求推进陷入僵局的解决缅甸危机和缓和南中国海紧张局势的努力，而几天后，世界各大国的高级外交官将齐聚一堂。</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jul 2024 06:03:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/asean-seeks-tackle-myanmar-crisis-south-china-sea-tension-ministers-meet-laos-2024-07-24/</guid></item><item><title>菲律宾命令离岸博彩中心的外籍工人两个月内离开</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-orders-foreign-workers-offshore-gaming-hubs-leave-2-months-2024-07-24/</link><description>菲律宾总统小费迪南德·马科斯决定取缔离岸赌博公司后，菲律宾移民局周三表示，该国已下令在离岸赌博公司工作的外国人在两个月内离开该国。</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jul 2024 05:25:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-orders-foreign-workers-offshore-gaming-hubs-leave-2-months-2024-07-24/</guid></item><item><title>独家：LG Energy Solution 正在与中国公司洽谈为欧洲生产低成本电动汽车电池</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/lg-energy-solution-talks-with-chinese-firms-make-low-cost-ev-batteries-europe-2024-07-24/</link><description>韩国 LG 能源解决方案公司 (LGES) 一位高管表示，正在与三个中国供应商就为欧洲生产低成本电动汽车电池进行谈判，欧盟对中国制造的电动汽车征收额外关税后，竞争将加剧。</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jul 2024 05:05:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/lg-energy-solution-talks-with-chinese-firms-make-low-cost-ev-batteries-europe-2024-07-24/</guid></item><item><title>中国量化基金在打击行动中遭受严重损失</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/chinas-quant-funds-suffer-deep-losses-amid-crackdown-2024-07-24/</link><description>数据显示，中国计算机驱动的“量化”对冲基金今年上半年遭受了严重损失，表现逊于国内传统股票策略和其他流行的全球基金策略。</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jul 2024 02:33:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/chinas-quant-funds-suffer-deep-losses-amid-crackdown-2024-07-24/</guid></item><item><title>亚洲股市在科技股盈利后波动，日元创七周高点</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-07-24/</link><description>美国科技巨头特斯拉和 Alphabet 的业绩不佳削弱了风险偏好，亚洲股市周三下跌，而在下周央行会议召开之前，日元飙升至七周高位，加息仍在讨论之中。</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jul 2024 02:26:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-07-24/</guid></item><item><title>中国盛和收购匹克稀土坦桑尼亚项目一半股权</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/chinas-shenghe-acquire-half-peak-rare-earths-tanzania-project-2024-07-24/</link><description>澳大利亚 Peak Rare Earths 周三表示，中国矿商盛和资源公司将收购一家英国公司 50% 的股份，该公司拥有其坦桑尼亚 Ngualla 项目 84% 的股权。</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jul 2024 00:44:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/chinas-shenghe-acquire-half-peak-rare-earths-tanzania-project-2024-07-24/</guid></item><item><title>台风“嘉美”接近台湾加强，工作暂停，航班取消</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-hunkers-down-ahead-arrival-typhoon-gaemi-2024-07-24/</link><description>周三，台湾因台风“高美”的到来而陷入困境，金融市场关闭，人们放假，航班取消，而军方在预计将有暴雨的情况下处于待命状态。</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jul 2024 00:23:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-hunkers-down-ahead-arrival-typhoon-gaemi-2024-07-24/</guid></item><item><title>独家：Nvidia 批准三星 HBM3 芯片用于中国市场处理器</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/nvidia-clears-samsungs-hbm3-chips-use-china-market-processor-sources-say-2024-07-23/</link><description>三名知情人士表示，三星电子的第四代高带宽内存或 HBM3 芯片已首次获得 Nvidia 批准用于其处理器。</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jul 2024 23:03:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/nvidia-clears-samsungs-hbm3-chips-use-china-market-processor-sources-say-2024-07-23/</guid></item><item><title>新日铁将解散与中国宝钢成立20年的合资企业</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/nippon-steel-dissolve-jv-with-chinas-baoshan-after-20-years-2024-07-23/</link><description>新日铁周二表示，将解散与中国宝山钢铁的合资企业，现有股东协议将于八月底到期，从而结束二十年的合作。</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jul 2024 22:57:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/nippon-steel-dissolve-jv-with-chinas-baoshan-after-20-years-2024-07-23/</guid></item><item><title>波音恢复向中国交付737 MAX飞机</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/boeing-resumes-deliveries-737-max-airplanes-china-2024-07-23/</link><description>波音公司周二表示，在因监管问题导致长时间延迟后，该公司已恢复向中国交付最畅销的 737 MAX 飞机。</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jul 2024 21:54:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/boeing-resumes-deliveries-737-max-airplanes-china-2024-07-23/</guid></item><item><title>渔业条约在世贸组织失败，引发中美担忧</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/fishing-treaty-fails-wto-prompting-us-chinese-concern-2024-07-23/</link><description>周二，削减渔业补贴的条约草案未能通过后，各国和环保组织表达了担忧和失望，中国呼吁各国对世界贸易组织的谈判方式进行重大改变。</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jul 2024 16:54:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/fishing-treaty-fails-wto-prompting-us-chinese-concern-2024-07-23/</guid></item><item><title>大众汽车在中国举步维艰。电动汽车能否帮助其在美国发展？</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/volkswagen-is-reeling-china-can-evs-help-it-grow-us-2024-07-23-2/</link><description>当大众集团上个月向美国电动卡车和 SUV 制造商 Rivian 投资 50 亿美元时，这家初创公司的股价因现金注入而飙升。</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jul 2024 12:59:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/volkswagen-is-reeling-china-can-evs-help-it-grow-us-2024-07-23-2/</guid></item><item><title>中国鼓励部分企业利用外债提振实体经济</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/china-encourages-some-firms-tap-foreign-debt-boost-real-economy-2024-07-23/</link><description>根据网上发布的官方声明，中国最高经济规划师周二表示，将支持优质企业借用中长期外债，支持实体经济发展。</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jul 2024 10:09:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/china-encourages-some-firms-tap-foreign-debt-boost-real-economy-2024-07-23/</guid></item><item><title>五角大楼表达担忧后，克里姆林宫表示俄罗斯与中国的北极合作不针对任何人</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/kremlin-says-russian-arctic-cooperation-with-china-is-not-aimed-against-anyone-2024-07-23/</link><description>克里姆林宫周二表示，俄罗斯与中国在北极的合作并不针对任何其他国家，并表示美国对此类工作的批评是错误的。</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jul 2024 09:53:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/kremlin-says-russian-arctic-cooperation-with-china-is-not-aimed-against-anyone-2024-07-23/</guid></item></channel></rss>